    "subtype": "spell",
    "targets": "1 creature",
    "text": "You call on Cobyslarni to open the target\u2019s mind to knowledge\u2014too much knowledge. The target\u2019s thoughts flood with irrelevant and confusing information, causing it to become stupefied 1 if it fails a Will save (or stupefied 2 on a critical failure).",
